post.body: Welcome to NYC and Happy Birthday!! You are going to have an amazing day. I can feel it.
I wish you safe travels and can't wait for you to get to your New City.
American Apparel has some with graphics that could pass or try Urban Outfitters.
I know but I've been extra naughts this year so my family was the last hope for gifts.
The 11 year old from last nights dinner? Yeah were totes friends now. Texting up a storm like BFF's.
Currently in a packed to the roof SUV with my brother, sister-in-law and Ellie, the 80 lb. lab
Just got back from the akward dinner party and I related with the 11 year old girl the most. Nice!
This is my favorite Christmas Song ever. Enjoy. ♫ http://blip.fm/~1atb4
So now I have to go to my sister-in-laws real Dad's house. I get to watch everyone open gifts while I twiddle my thumbs. Akward!!
I got a Howard Finster original from my parents. Best Gift Ever!!!
Merry Christmas to old friends, new friends and future friends!
So far I've gotten four bottles of wine from my sister-in-law's family. Umm...
I want Darlene Love to marry me.
I was 1% away from winning Wii American Idol marathon. CrapCakes!!!
Have arrived in Macon to more Doggies!
"and your shape on the dance floor will have me thinking such filth I'll gouge my eyes" ♫ http://blip.fm/~1a1va
Really Facebook? Site maintenance? What, too many holiday photos overloading you?
Injecting coffee. Showering & packing need to happen. We are taking this Sery Christmastime Spectacular on the road. Next stop..Macon, GA.
